Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:27.97,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an2}片源：10thMystery   翻译：L. / 尘焱\N校对：KaNeyome   后期：yulius   繁化：塔布里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:27.97,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}本字幕由澄空学园字幕组制作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:17.13,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心では何度も　好きと伝えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:27.60,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想いは残るの？　わたし消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:37.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君の声　真っ直ぐな瞳　忘れない温もり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:46.34,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}記憶の中に閉じ込めたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:52.65,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}変えられないこと　変えてしまいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:23:02.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}何度でも運命の中を　笑いあって　ふざけあって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.23,0:23:08.68,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}「明日また会えるよね」　きっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:19.76,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}会いたい　ただひとつだけ願い叶うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:17.13,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在心中曾千百次  向你表述过爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:27.60,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}是否会留下情思  即便我终会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:37.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你的声响  直视的目光  是无法忘怀的暖阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:46.34,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想要烙刻在记忆上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:52.65,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}无从改变之物  却又想要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:23:02.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不断在轮回命运中  一同嬉笑  一同玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.23,0:23:08.68,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一定能够「明天再会」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:19.76,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}愿与你相会  若这唯一的祈愿将能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态好像是稳定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他们说佳织恢复意识的几率几乎为零
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:32.98,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)\pos(603,302)}『通向过去的大门』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后  我们根本就没心思再办天象馆咖啡厅了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果直到那年的文化节结束都无所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之后  凪沙学姐又告诉我古川结转学的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  偶尔也来一下学会露个脸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学年主任很担心你  老是问我「那家伙将来的目标要怎么办」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  我也明白你的心情  但再不调整的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来会长决定好要做什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定要进内滨大学的理科学部了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我建议的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪沙学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打算做一些自己能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  你的打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了寻找治好佳织的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定去读医学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考上医大的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时离开了有着和佳织一起的回忆的家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大学里我很快就碰壁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想让佳织苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须对大脑进行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对于采用对症疗法的现代医学来说是难以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑是未知的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他部位有了损伤的话  可以移植
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理论上也是可能再生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有脑是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  现在正在研究量子图灵机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子图灵机？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中的时候有个老师上课时经常扯到那个  不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那时候只觉得老师不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,概括地说就是把那个从理论转化为实践
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简而言之  脑可能就是一台量子图灵机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像是抓住了救命稻草一样  研究量子论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至开始去研究量子控制论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我才知道这和诗织阿姨的研究有很大的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只听说自从佳织出事后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织阿姨好像在热衷于某项特别的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了好几年  佳织仍旧沉睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  在的话我就进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借你的厨房用用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KENNY好像又寄来新的报告了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是关于宇宙弦向额外维空间延伸的时间逆行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像说梦话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟简单说来就是回到过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真能做到  那个叫什么时间悖论的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会引发什么谁也不清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凪沙学姐打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  令人怀念的我的母校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么要在这里申请建新的研究所？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的地方也没什么不方便的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我常常带到活动室来的黑色的盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  记得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从当时开始大家就一直在研究那个盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是随着调查的深入发现它在特定的地方才会有很强的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方就是这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不惜废弃学校也要继续研究  太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个能再陪陪我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华宫综合研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里对那个黑盒子进行着研究
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外  在很多其他领域的研究上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是世界上最尖端的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理  也欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织阿姨  那个东西马上就能看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是研究所里进行着最高机密研究的部门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  诗织阿姨她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是研究团队的成员之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是在研究什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想还是亲眼看一看比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好厉害  简直就像是SF一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个中间的地方就是最高机密？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  古川吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是曾经叫做结的东西  这么说比较妥当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结怎么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天  佳织遇到事故的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回到家后  发现结睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是机能停止运转了  这样说更加准确吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结  你已经回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要太担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作之进  作之进  拜托  快来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织跟我说她弄丢了  为什么会在结这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结可能跟那场事故有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这为什么成了最高机密？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说她不是人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说  她是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以现在的技术  她是不可能被造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底是谁制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然出现在内滨学园里  又为什么突然停止运转了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是些未知的迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么一直都瞒着我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时因为佳织的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有说出来的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(351,323)\fs18}AI Unit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们研究团队发现那个叫做AI智能体的黑盒子对结有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结跟那个盒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在研究她的过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了拯救佳织的一个可能的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了拯救佳织的可能的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结的人造生物器官非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内脏  血管  从神经系统到大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  她的脑跟人类的脑有差不多的机能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么诗织阿姨找到的能救佳织的方法就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过研究她的身体  造一个新的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把佳织移到那个身体里去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把佳织移过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大脑里的信息  包括意识全部移植过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子图灵机  但是那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情理论上可行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你们能参与这个研究
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和爱理从大学退了学  加入了诗织阿姨的团队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了制造新的素体的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(351,323)\fs18}Yui's Unforced Intelligence system
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是结的主动智能系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为YUIs工程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理主攻AI智能体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来研究结的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造结所用的技术是让人震撼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究飞快地进行着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又过了几年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于  新的人造素体诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了这个时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始进行佐佐木佳织的意识转移
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始连接接口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认量子新脑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始量子纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑波正常  心跳数正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素体的机能也开始运转了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  信息转移不进素体的人造大脑里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样  不应该会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下机器  终止移植
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除量子纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:11:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织的意识明明没有移动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素体却有了意识活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一素体已经无法用来移植了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织阿姨要去国外是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在北欧有个研究人造大脑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织阿姨还没放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那种方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人会怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山他也差不多该下结论了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然支仓小姐就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山他到现在为止一直都一心想着佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像完全没注意到支仓小姐的感情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为会因实验失败而告一段落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女之间的关系就是有这么复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就说三次元好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  广
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙弦向额外维空间延伸的时间逆行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟简单说来就是回到过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以现在的技术  她是不可能被造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  现在正在研究量子图灵机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我常常带到活动室来的黑色的盒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着调查的深入发现它在特定的地方才会有很强的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太愚蠢了  明明如此愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么每一个细节都严丝合缝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支仓小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山他还闷在房间里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来啦  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是爱理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是睡在这种地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心身体吃不消哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有样东西想给爱理看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织的素体被…  被整形成结的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变过去  从而拯救佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么改变过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把结送到佳织出事之前那段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她阻止事故的发生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:16:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是在说时间移动这种虚构的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前KENNY送来的他那边的研究人员的论文？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只不过是没有任何依据的理论而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信有时间逆行这一回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结改变了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但世界也不过是产生了分歧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的佳织并不会被拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在分歧之后还会有汇合的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汇合？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果的锁链会修正这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而总有一天悖论也会就此消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果的锁链  这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理你真的会相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物理学家在世界的一隅每做一次猫的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中的物理总量就会翻倍这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是多重世界诠释吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从宇宙总体那压倒性的物质量来看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是只要花数十年就可以恢复的误差而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要资料遗失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并从研究人员的记忆中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界便会再次汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了资源的有效利用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有力量使产生分歧的世界再度汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自然的规律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说这就是因果的锁链吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  但是想要用这个方法回到过去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收的地方也必须要有个量子传送装置才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AI智能体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个盒子会在特定的地点发出细微的量子震动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而反应最强烈的地方就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧校舍的五楼原本是电梯的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是结出现的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底结到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由不可能实现的技术创造出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会对被称为AI智能体的黑盒子产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她究竟是为了什么而出现的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的呢  动机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候真的丧失记忆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那奇怪的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的假说中的推论全部相吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  你没疯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  结
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是地球仪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球仪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球仪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes  地球仪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险  真的好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的空气真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在地面上看见的星辰的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很久以前发出的光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙女座银河距离地球是239万光年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在所见到的是239万年前的光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和239万年相比  14年只不过是眨眼一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间拖得越长  和过去的距离就会变得越远
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所需的能量也会变得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前的模拟演示相比
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的进程比想象的慢了很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没精神了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么成功不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说最初的结是谁做出来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AI智能体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始果然还是分析了那个盒子之后的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  应该是诗织阿姨做出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那AI智能体呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个量子图灵机也许就是记录多重世界的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿克夏记录差不多的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会对身为分歧点的结产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了结以外的人则不被允许做时间逆行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为记录点…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是记录点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要把你送回到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从10月14日发生的事故中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出佐佐木佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就留在这里看门了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就分头调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织…
